NOTE ON ASSETS

The MIT license above covers the SOURCE CODE of this project (Board.gd and the
project files). It does NOT cover the assets below, which are kept under their
own terms. Full details and links are in CREDITS.md.

- The Blipo name and the Blip artwork and playfield art are by Sarah Copeland
  and are not licensed for reuse.
- Sound effects: JDSherbert "Pixel Game Essentials SFX Pack" (Free Pack),
  https://jdsherbert.itch.io/pixel-game-essentials-sfx-pack
- Music: Pudgyplatypus, "Royalty Free Game Music Loops" (OpenGameArt),
  https://opengameart.org/content/royalty-free-game-music-loops
- UI art: Crusenho "Complete UI Essential Pack", licensed CC BY 4.0,
  https://crusenho.itch.io (attribution required).
- Fonts: Modak, Play, and Marck Script (Google Fonts, SIL Open Font License).

If you fork this repo, keep the attribution each asset's license requires, or
replace the assets with your own.
